<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:32:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普试图推翻选举失败的后果将提交给最高法院</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fallout-from-trumps-bid-to-overturn-election-loss-heads-to-supreme-court/articleshow/109287527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国最高法院就特朗普试图避免起诉和袭击国会大厦的指控提起诉讼。费舍尔面临阻碍。特朗普的封口费审判开始。法院推翻了科罗拉多州的裁决。特朗普声称拥有总统豁免权。法律专家预计审判结果将在 11 月 5 日之前公布。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 10:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fallout-from-trumps-bid-to-overturn-election-loss-heads-to-supreme-court/articleshow/109287527.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击以色列后俄罗斯敦促“克制”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/russia-urges-restraint-after-iranian-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109287334.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287334.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在伊朗对以色列进行导弹和无人机袭击后，俄罗斯呼吁保持克制。莫斯科对事态升级表示担忧，并指出中东局势可能会加剧不稳定。俄罗斯外长拉夫罗夫与伊朗阿米尔-阿卜杜拉希安进行了交谈。俄罗斯外交部表示，拉夫罗夫重申“坚决谴责”以色列本月在叙利亚发动的袭击，造成伊朗将军死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/russia-urges-restraint-after-iranian-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109287334.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃及否认关闭领空并确认继续空中航行</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-denies-closure-of-its-airspace-and-confirms-continuation-of-air-navigation/articleshow/109287187.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109287187.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃及政府驳斥了埃及领空被关闭的说法。埃及内阁媒体中心今天表示，除飞往空域关闭国家的航班外，埃及所有机场均正常运行，航班继续按计划飞行。尽管社交媒体和某些媒体上流传着谣言，但该中心保证空中航行不会中断。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/egypt-denies-closure-of-its-airspace-and-confirms-continuation-of-air-navigation/articleshow/109287187.cms</guid></item><item><title>悉尼袭击中丧生的巴基斯坦男子：社区团体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistani-man-among-those-killed-in-sydney-attack-community-groups/articleshow/109285960.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285960.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据两个当地社区团体称，一名 30 岁的巴基斯坦男子周日在悉尼一家购物中心周末持刀袭击中丧生，这名保安是一名保安。澳大利亚巴基斯坦全国协会和艾哈迈迪亚穆斯林社区表示，法拉兹·塔希尔被一名持刀男子杀害，该男子还杀害了五名妇女。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistani-man-among-those-killed-in-sydney-attack-community-groups/articleshow/109285960.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列“仍在拦截伊朗的巡航导弹”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-still-intercepting-cruise-missiles-in-iranian-barrage/articleshow/109286958.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286958.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;当伊朗用无人机和导弹发动攻击时，以色列国防军在境外拦截巡航导弹。美军发射200多枚导弹，拦截无人机。乔丹击落无人机。 10 岁女孩被掉落的弹片炸伤。箭3防空系统成功拦截弹道导弹。伊朗警告美国不要支持以色列。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:30:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-still-intercepting-cruise-missiles-in-iranian-barrage/articleshow/109286958.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰对俄罗斯控制城镇的袭击造成16人死亡：官方</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-attack-on-russia-controlled-town-kills-16-official/articleshow/109285806.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285806.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰扎波罗热地区托克马克军事炮击造成的死亡人数已达16人，其中20人受伤，12人伤势严重。俄罗斯任命的官员叶夫根尼·巴利茨基 (Yevgeny Balitsky) 在 Telegram 上分享了这一信息。这些事件未经路透社证实，乌克兰也没有做出回应。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-attack-on-russia-controlled-town-kills-16-official/articleshow/109285806.cms</guid></item><item><title>索马里海盗索要500万美元赎金后释放被劫持的MV Abdullah船</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/somali-pirates-release-hijacked-ship-mv-abdullah-after-5-million-ransom/articleshow/109286477.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286477.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;索马里海盗在收到500万美元赎金后释放了被劫持的MV Abdullah船。海盗们验证了这笔钱，将其分割，并躲避了政府军的追捕。索马里政府尚未发表评论。悬挂孟加拉国国旗的“阿卜杜拉”号于三月在前往阿联酋的途中被扣押，标志着海盗活动死灰复燃。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/somali-pirates-release-hijacked-ship-mv-abdullah-after-5-million-ransom/articleshow/109286477.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警方确认了导致6人死亡的悉尼刺伤袭击者身份</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vigil-held-for-victims-of-sydney-mall-attack/articleshow/109286711.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286711.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;悉尼为乔尔·考奇持刀袭击的受害者举行守夜活动。哀悼者在韦斯特菲尔德购物中心表达哀悼。引用的心理健康问题。父母表达悲痛。社区哀悼罕见的暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 09:22:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vigil-held-for-victims-of-sydney-mall-attack/articleshow/109286711.cms</guid></item><item><title>苏丹长达一年的冲突引发大规模饥饿威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sudans-year-long-conflict-spurs-mass-starvation-threat/articleshow/109286470.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286470.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;苏丹面临着严峻的人道主义危机，冲突、暴行不断升级，饥荒威胁迫在眉睫。奥麦玛·法鲁克 (Omaima Farouq) 和她的孩子们在一个缺乏国际援助的小村庄里忍受着苦难。报告显示，暴力、流离失所和粮食不安全现象普遍存在，造成 14,600 多人丧生，数百万人流离失所。全球紧急干预对于防止大规模伤亡至关重要。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sudans-year-long-conflict-spurs-mass-starvation-threat/articleshow/109286470.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊拉克、约旦和黎巴嫩重新开放因伊朗袭击以色列而关闭的领空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iraq-jordan-lebanon-reopen-airspace-closed-over-iran-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109286396.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286396.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊拉克在因伊朗无人机和导弹袭击以色列而暂停航班后重新开放领空。事件发生后，约旦、黎巴嫩和以色列也恢复了空中交通。以色列报告称拦截了伊朗的大部分发射。伊拉克北部库尔德媒体报道称，伊朗无人机连夜飞越库尔德自治区上空。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:55:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iraq-jordan-lebanon-reopen-airspace-closed-over-iran-attack-on-israel/articleshow/109286396.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯超音速导弹艇进入地中海</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russian-supersonic-missile-boat-enters-mediterranean/articleshow/109286198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109286198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:41:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russian-supersonic-missile-boat-enters-mediterranean/articleshow/109286198.cms</guid></item><item><title>南非总统拉马福萨敦促穆斯林社区成员积极参与政治</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-african-president-ramaphosa-urges-muslim-community-members-to-join-active-politics/articleshow/109285738.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285738.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拉马福萨敦促印度裔穆斯林在劳迪姆举行的重要开斋节集会上积极参与争取平等的政治活动。他承认过去的领导人并呼吁团结起来重建南非。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-african-president-ramaphosa-urges-muslim-community-members-to-join-active-politics/articleshow/109285738.cms</guid></item><item><title>悉尼商场持刀行凶 母亲牺牲自己交出婴儿</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dying-mother-sacrifices-own-life-hands-over-baby-in-sydney-mall-stabbing-rampage/articleshow/109285715.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285715.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在悉尼购物中心持刀伤人事件中，目击者讲述了一位母亲阿什莉·古德 (Ashlee Good) 的绝望行为，她为拯救九个月大的婴儿哈丽特 (Harriet) 牺牲了自己的生命，出现了令人心碎的勇敢行为。当袭击者在购物中心接近他们时，38 岁的古德将受伤的婴儿交给了一名陌生人。不幸的是，古德在医院因伤重不治身亡，死亡人数上升至六人。然而，经过数小时的手术后，她的孩子仍然处于严重但稳定的状态。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dying-mother-sacrifices-own-life-hands-over-baby-in-sydney-mall-stabbing-rampage/articleshow/109285715.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称哈马斯在伊朗袭击后拒绝停火提议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-hamas-rejected-cease-fire-proposal-after-iran-attack/articleshow/109285775.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285775.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据以色列外部情报机构摩萨德称，伊朗支持的激进组织哈马斯拒绝了调解人提出的纲要。虽然摩萨德没有直接指出伊朗对以色列的无人机和导弹袭击是罪魁祸首，但它表示，哈马斯在加沙的领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔“继续利用与伊朗的紧张关系”，并且“不希望达成人道主义协议和返回”人质的。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-hamas-rejected-cease-fire-proposal-after-iran-attack/articleshow/109285775.cms</guid></item><item><title>悉尼持刀袭击者有心理健康问题，意识形态而非动机：警方</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sydney-knife-attacker-had-mental-health-issues-ideology-not-motive-police/articleshow/109285497.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285497.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;悉尼 Westfield Bondi Junction 购物中心发生悲惨刺伤事件，造成 6 人死亡、12 人受伤。袭击者乔尔·考奇(Joel Cauchi)有心理健康问题史，没有明显的意识形态动机。艾米·斯科特督察勇敢地面对并开枪打死了他。社区哀悼遇难者并赞扬勇敢的行为。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 08:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/sydney-knife-attacker-had-mental-health-issues-ideology-not-motive-police/articleshow/109285497.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对希特勒的迷恋是 1930 年代的不祥回响</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-hitler-fascination-is-an-ominous-echo-of-the-1930s/articleshow/109285025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109285025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着强势领导人越来越受欢迎，民主面临全球挑战，这让人想起法西斯主义盛行的黑暗时代。习近平、普京、欧尔班、莫迪和特朗普等独裁人物让人想起过去的独裁者。对民选领导人的信任正在下降，这与 20 世纪 30 年代的历史相似。尽管存在危险，强人统治的吸引力依然存在。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 07:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-hitler-fascination-is-an-ominous-echo-of-the-1930s/articleshow/109285025.cms</guid></item><item><title>七国集团领导人周日视频通话讨论伊朗袭击事件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/g7-leaders-to-discuss-iranian-attack-in-sunday-video-call/articleshow/109284353.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109284353.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:46:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/g7-leaders-to-discuss-iranian-attack-in-sunday-video-call/articleshow/109284353.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国对伊朗袭击以色列后局势升级“深感担忧”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-deeply-concerned-about-escalation-after-iran-strikes-israel/articleshow/109284008.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109284008.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国对中东紧张局势深表关切，强调伊朗袭击以色列领土后需要保持冷静和克制。强调解决加沙冲突紧张局势的紧迫性，以防止冲突风险扩大。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-deeply-concerned-about-escalation-after-iran-strikes-israel/articleshow/109284008.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列的多层防空系统保护其免受伊朗无人机和导弹袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-multilayered-air-defense-system-protected-it-from-irans-drone-and-missile-strike/articleshow/109282594.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109282594.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在针对哈马斯的六个月战争中，以色列的防空系统在美国和英国的支持下，成功抵御了来自 300 多架伊朗无人机和弹道导弹的重大威胁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-multilayered-air-defense-system-protected-it-from-irans-drone-and-missile-strike/articleshow/109282594.cms</guid></item><item><title>不受欢迎的里希·苏纳克陷入“末日循环”，英国首相的胜利存疑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/unpopular-rishi-sunak-in-doom-loop-as-uk-pms-victory-in-doubt/articleshow/109282105.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109282105.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国保守党领袖兼首相里希·苏纳克面临着支持率下降和赢得即将到来的大选的不确定性。尽管减税和经济略有改善，但鲍里斯·约翰逊的批评、英国脱欧的不确定性和公众的不满情绪构成了重大障碍。随着选举的不确定性迫在眉睫，苏纳克的领导层正在努力应对不断变化的政治潮流。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/unpopular-rishi-sunak-in-doom-loop-as-uk-pms-victory-in-doubt/articleshow/109282105.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>